Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend Index VIT Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 8:15 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend Index VIT Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend Index VIT Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity indexed mutual fund launched by Northern Lights Variable Trust. The fund is managed by W.E. Donoghue & Co., Llc. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in dividend paying stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. The fund replicates the performance of its portfolio against the W.E. Donoghue Power Dividend Index. It was formerly known as Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend Index Portfolio. Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend I...
Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend Index VIT Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity indexed mutual fund launched by Northern Lights Variable Trust. The fund is managed by W.E. Donoghue & Co., Llc. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in dividend paying stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. The fund replicates the performance of its portfolio against the W.E. Donoghue Power Dividend Index. It was formerly known as Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend Index Portfolio. Northern Lights Variable Trust - Power Dividend Index VIT Fund was formed on May 1, 2007 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


, MA United StatesFounded in 2007










